      "<h3>\n\nHealth Systems Evidence also wishes to acknowledge the following groups that prepare the user-friendly summaries that we provide links to:\n\n</h3><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Australasian Cochrane Centre (ACC) Policy Liaison Initiative&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.cochrane.org.au%2fprojects%2fpolicy.php'>\n\nAustralasian Cochrane Centre (ACC) Policy Liaison Initiative\n\n</a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Database of Review of Effects (DARE)&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.york.ac.uk%2finst%2fcrd%2f'>Database of Review of Effects (DARE)\n\n</a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Effective Health Care Research Programme Consortium &L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.evidence4health.org'>\n\nEffective Health Care Research Programme Consortium\n\n</a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Evidence Aid&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.cochrane.org%2fcochrane-reviews%2fevidence-aid-project'>\n\nEvidence Aid\n\n</a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Health Knowledge Network of the Cochrane Consumers and Communications Review Group (CC&CRG) Evidence Bulletins&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.latrobe.edu.au%2fchcp%2fhkn%2findex.html'>\n\nHealth Knowledge Network of the Cochrane Consumers <br />and Communications Review Group (CC&CRG) Evidence Bulletins\n\n</a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Healthevidence.org&L=http%3a%2f%2fhealthevidence.org%2f'>\n\nHealthevidence.org\n\n</a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Reproductive Health Library&L=http%3a%2f%2fapps.who.int%2frhl%2fen%2f'>\n\nReproductive Health Library\n\n</a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Rx for Change&L=http%3a%2f%2fcadth.ca%2fresources%2frx-for-change'>\n\nRx for Change\n\n</a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=SUPPORT Collaboration&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.support-collaboration.org%2f'>\n\nSUPPORT Collaboration\n\n</a></p>",
