    en:
      "The original development of Health Systems Evidence focused on document types 2-4, with eligible documents identified through searches for Medline from the Cochrane Collaboration’s Effective Practice and Organization of Care (EPOC) review groups and a hand search of 15 journals likely to contain qualitative reviews, as well as a number of additional sources.",
